en really liking lobster and New England seafood and Tex-mex and Mexican food.\", \"from\": 626, \"to\": 740, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 715, \"end\": 722, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tex-Mex\", \"score\": 0.9998238341607679, \"rank\": 0.00017619687906100573, \"text\": \"Tex-mex\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tex-Mex\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tex-Mex\"}, {\"begin\": 727, \"end\": 739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexican_cuisine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.3688415680014577e-17, \"text\": \"Mexican food\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexican_cuisine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexican_cuisine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Taco Cabana.\", \"from\": 741, \"to\": 753, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 741, \"end\": 752, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taco_Cabana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Taco Cabana\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taco_Cabana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taco_Cabana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am always talking about Taco Cabana.\\\"\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 793, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 780, \"end\": 791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taco_Cabana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Taco Cabana\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taco_Cabana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taco_Cabana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sanderson will be competing in the Olympics and representing Team USA for the fourth time this year.\", \"from\": 795, \"to\": 895, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 795, \"end\": 804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_William_Sanderson\", \"score\": 0.7819102661943991, \"rank\": 0.2756567536920536, \"text\": \"Sanderson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_William_Sanderson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_William_Sanderson\"}, {\"begin\": 856, \"end\": 864, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.9620793092401227, \"rank\": 0.03899730667831039, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His first was back at the 2008 Beijing games, where heentered the final round with the lead, but ended up finishing fifth.\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 1018, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 922, \"end\": 934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999998331077, \"rank\": 1.667575161696953e-10, \"text\": \"2008 Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"{sd-embed class=\\\"sd-embedded-media\\\" data-alt=\\\"FINALS%20-3.jpg\\\" data-caption=\\\"Photo%20by%7B%7DJoshua%20Schave/USA%20Shooting\\\" data-duration=\\\"\\\" data-externalid=\\\"c1682a95-ea33-430c-b643-94f4872677b0\\\" data-mediatype=\\\"image\\\" data-renditions=\\\"%7B%22large16x9%22:%7B%22blurSigma%22:-1,%22height%22:3255,%22label%22:%22large16x9%22,%22scaleWidth%22:986,%22url%22:%22/resources/media2/16x9/5784/986/0x598/90/c1682a95-ea33-430c-b643-94f4872677b0-FINALS3.jpg%22,%22width%22:5784,%22x%22:0,%22y%22:598,%22uuid%22:null,%22id%22:%22b3876afc-0967-46fe-92ea-5d522f67d48e%22,%22preciseWidth%22:null,%22preciseHeight%22:null,%22name%22:%22large16x9Url%22,%22rendition%22:%22large16x9%22,%22labelOrConvertedName%22:%22large16x9%22%7D,%22jumbo16x9%22:%7B%22blurSigma%22:-1,%22height%22:3255,%22label%22:%22jumbo16x9%22,%22scaleWidth%22:1320,%22url%22:%22/resources/media2/16x9/5784/1320/0x598/90/c1682a95-ea33-430c-b643-94f4872677b0-FINALS3.jpg%22,%22width%22:5784,%22x%22:0,%22y%22:598,%22uuid%22:null,%22id%22:%22266